import React from 'react'; import Layout from '../components/Layout/Layout'; const Admissions= () => { return (

Admissions

Welcome to the admissions page of our school. Here you will find all the information you need to apply.

Admissions Process

Our admissions process is designed to be straightforward and transparent. Please follow the steps below:

  1. Complete the online application form.
  2. Submit required documents.
  3. Attend an interview (if applicable).
  4. Receive admission decision.

Requirements

To apply, you will need the following:

  • Completed application form
  • Transcripts from previous schools
  • Letters of recommendation
  • Personal statement

Important Dates

Make sure to note the following important dates:

  • Application Deadline: March 1
  • Interviews: March 15 - March 30
  • Decision Notification: April 15
 ); }; export default Admissions;
